 can accelerate from  kmh in  seconds production is limited to  units unlike the veyron the chiron is expected to make a profit citationsedit  a b c volkswagen ag  p   a b c volkswagen ag  p   a b c volkswagen ag  p   cremer   bbc   bugatti chiron to have eightyear lifespan sell at a profit motor authority retrieved    bugatti chiron  finally a profitable model says boss paul tans automotive news retrieved    hetzner christiaan bugatti chiron to be priced at  million is ready for a new world speed record automotive news retrieved    bugatti chiron price specs and full details on the bhp hypercar auto express retrieved   referencesedit volkswagen aktiengesellschaft facts and figures  pdf volkswagenagcom volkswagen aktiengesellschaft   archived pdf from the original on  retrieved   cremer andreas  bugatti said to get backing for  million galibier supercar bloomberg business week new york city new york bloomberg lp issn  archived from the original on  retrieved   bbc two  top gear series  episode  bbc  retrieved   see alsoedit france portal cars portal companies portal list of car brands external linksedit media related to bugatti automobiles vehicles at wikimedia commons official website v t e bugatti a subsidiary of volkswagen ag since  bugatti automobiles –present current cars chiron past cars veyron concept cars eb  eb   chiron c galibier vision gran turismo bugatti automobili – road cars eb  eb  people romano artioli automobiles ettore bugatti – road cars type  type  cylinder line type  type  type  type  type  type  type  royale type  type  type  type  type  type  racing cars type  type  type  type  type  type  type  type  type  people ettore bugatti founder jean bugatti roland bugatti bugatti automobiles official website category commons v t e « previous bugatti a brand of the volkswagen group since  road car timeline s–present type – s s s s                                owner defunct romano artioli volkswagen group company name bugatti automobili spa bugatti a