ngine delivering  horse power and an electronically limited top speed of  miles per hour and a price of about € the chiron attempts to vastly surpass the veyrons performance concept carsedit italdesign giugiaro designsedit volkswagen commissioned italdesigns giorgetto giugiaro to design a series of concept cars to return the marque to prominence the first example the eb  was a twodoor coupé and was introduced at the paris motor show in  it was followed by the fourdoor eb  touring sedan introduced at the geneva motor show in  later that year the  chiron was shown at the iaa in frankfurt volkswagen designsedit volkswagen designed the final bugatti concept the eb  gt in house bugatti introduced the eb  at the  tokyo motor show w engineedit all of these early concepts featured a  ps  kw  hp cylinder engine this was the firstever wconfiguration engine on a passenger vehicle with three blocks of  cylinders each it shared many components with volkswagens modular engine family c galibieredit main article bugatti c galibier the c galibier was first unveiled during celebration of the centenary of the marque in molsheim the presentation was only for bugatti customers the car show in molsheim showed the car in blue carbon fibre and aluminum parts one year later bugatti showed the world the c galibier concept at vw group night at the geneva auto show in a new black and aluminum color combination the galibier a  hp sedan was first shown as a concept in  and when they planned to put it into production in  it would have cost about  million it would use the same cylinder litre engine as the veyron but instead of four turbos the c galibier would instead use two superchargers to deliver better torque production would require new facilities in molsheim france to be refitted which pushed back potential deliveries until  in  it was announced that the car will never be produced as they wish to focus on a veyron replacement production carsedit bugatti eb gt in the s the bugatti brand was b